with version stable 1.2.18 1.2.16 1.2.15 1.2.14 1.2.5
with base    Python potrace t1utils
with role    font/editor
with trait   console
with source  http://lilypond.org/download/sources/mftrace/mftrace-$VERSION.tar.gz
with info    last 20120510
with info    home http://lilypond.org/mftrace/
with info    cite 'converts TeX bitmap fonts into PFA or PFB fonts
mftrace is a small Python program that lets you
trace a TeX bitmap font into a PFA or PFB font
(A PostScript Type1 Scalable Font) or TTF (TrueType) font.'
